

# Feature:


1. backup a configure file
2. list the backup file
3. download configure file
4. delete configure file

## API:


1. Backup

Method: POST

URI: http://backup.securepilot.com/rest/v1/backup

Parameter:


2. List backup

Method: POST

URI: http://backup.securepilot.com/rest/v1/list


3. Download

Method: POST

URI: http://backup.securepilot.com/rest/v1/download


## Autoscale rule:

TBD
CPU up to 90%



## Auto start:

pm2 startup ubuntu
pm2 save

## Start

pm2 start backup.js



